## LAYOUT RULES

- Max content width: 1400px, centered with margin 0 auto.
- Card padding: 16-24px. Never less than 12px.
- Card border-radius: 12-16px. Consistent across all cards.
- Gap between cards: 16-20px using CSS grid or flex gap.
- Section spacing: 32-48px between major sections.
- Use CSS Grid for card layouts: gridTemplateColumns repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)).
- Use Flexbox for horizontal alignment within cards.
- Custom scrollbar: thin, dark, matching theme.

## INTERACTIVE PATTERNS

### Click-through Steps

- useState for current step index.
- Previous/Next buttons or clickable step indicators.
- Active step gets accent border + glow. Inactive steps are muted.
- Content transitions with slideUp keyed to step change.

### Expandable Sections

- useState(null) for active panel.
- Click toggles open/close. Only one section open at a time.
- Content appears with slideUp animation.

### Hover Effects

- Cards: border-color changes to accent on hover.
- Buttons: background lightens by changing opacity suffix (18 to 28).
- Never use transform scale on hover. Too aggressive.

